 &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">5.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">具有良好的商业信誉</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; background: white; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">6.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">近三年内在经营活动中无严重不良记录</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; background: white; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: red; background: white;\">7.</span><span style=\"color: red; background: white;\">第一次公告中已报名的无需再报名</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; background: white; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">8.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">报名截止时间：<span>2023</span>年<span>8 </span>月<span> 8</span>日<span> 24</span>：<span>00</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; background: white; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">联系人：唐老师联系方式：<span>18921892789&nbsp; </span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; background: white; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: red; background: white;\">9.</span><span style=\"color: red; background: white;\">具体遴选时间，另行通知</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">。</span></